Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:29.80,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}把这样的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:33.02,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}吹き飛ばすきっかけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:33.02,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}全部吹飞的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.92,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}招くばかりの指先を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.92,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}吸引而来的指尖
